com.rscja.deviceapi

Class Fingerprint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rscja.deviceapi.Fingerprint

  • public class Fingerprint
extends java.lang.Object
    指纹识别模块操作类,
    Fingerprint identify module operation type

    注意：
    Note:
    1、使用前请确认您的机器已安装此模块。
    1. Please make sure this module is installed in your device before using.
    2、要正常使用模块需要在\libs\armeabi\目录放置libDeviceAPI.so文件
    2. Put libDeviceAPI.so file in directory \libs\armeabi\ then module can be used normally.
    3、在操作设备前需要调用 init() 打开设备，使用完后调用 free() 关闭设备
    3. Before operating the device, call init() to switch on the device, then call free() to switch off the device.

    Author:
    liuruifeng
